30
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:45,580
Your moods are fluctuating constantly.

31
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:48,460
You're soon to be a mother, after all.

32
00:02:54,460 --> 00:02:58,570
I really should be feeling more jubilant about your trip.

33
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:03,340
Is it because no one will nag at you about what you can't do anymore?

34
