But I feel really upset right now!

35
00:03:16,380 --> 00:03:20,100
Husband, don't come back too soon.

36
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:21,880
What?

37
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:24,390
I still want to take a bite out of you.

38
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,830
Husband...

39
00:03:43,670 --> 00:03:47,960
Husband... Husband!

40
00:03:50,460 --> 00:03:53,340
- What's the matter? <br> - Mother! Where's my husband?

41
00:03:53,340 --> 00:03:56,300
Son-in-Law has entered the palace already.

42
00:03:56,300 --> 00:03:58,450
I thought he'd left without saying goodbye.

43
00:03:58,450 --> 00:04:01,260
- How could he have done that? Silly child. <br> - He scared me to death.

44
00:04:01,260 --> 00:04:04,270
Go and get cleaned up. Let's go.

45
00:04:04,860 --> 00:04:08,600
Lord Yongning is returning to the border's pass once again.

46
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:11,070
May you obtain instant success.

47
00:04:12,290 --> 00:04:13,860
Yes.

48
00:04:17,650 --> 00:04:20,380
Your Majesty, the State Treasury is empty.

49
00:04:20,380 --> 00:04:22,550
After resolving the previous conflict at the frontier fortress,

50
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:25,920
we'd already done our best by sending the military supply wagons over.

51
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:28,690
We really cannot afford to fork out much anymore.

52
00:04:28,690 --> 00:04:30,640
Then, how much more can we withdraw?

53
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:34,170
There isn't much left after we sent the disaster relief fund to Shu. <i>(T/N Shu area is today's Sichuan province)</i>

54
00:04:34,170 --> 00:04:38,620
Are you saying our men should starve while they go to battle?

55
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:44,390
Those are merely the soldiers who are left from the previous battle.

56
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:47,540
And besides, Deputy General will still be there defending the frontier fortress.

57
00:04:47,540 --> 00:04:51,520
This subject feels there is no need for Lord Yongning to journey there.

58
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:53,790
If the palace sends someone to specifically battle them,

59
00:04:53,790 --> 00:04:56,960
then it would appear as if the court attaches too much importance to this matter.

60
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:59,430
It'll seem like we're making a big deal out of a minor situation.

61
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:02,550
Besides, the funds from the State Treasury have all been used up. We really can't afford it.

62
00:05:02,550 --> 00:05:06,030
Lord Yongning, what are your thoughts on this?

63
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:09,170
This subject will obey all of Your Majesty's commands.

