76
00:06:38,850 --> 00:06:40,600
<i>Husband?</i>

77
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:46,130
<i>What I want to know is,</i>

78
00:06:46,130 --> 00:06:50,520
<i>how does this husband of yours compare to your Elder Sister Ruonan?</i>

79
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:52,160
<i>You're just so–</i>

80
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:54,010
<i>What are you doing?</i>

81
00:06:54,010 --> 00:06:57,320
<i>It seems if I don't enforce a husband's authority on you a little,</i>

82
00:06:57,320 --> 00:07:00,410
<i>then you won't pay attention to me anymore.</i>

83
00:07:04,460 --> 00:07:06,320
<i>Chu Xiuming!</i>

84
00:07:13,610 --> 00:07:18,490
<i>I wonder if the general is having a hard time.</i>

85
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:23,520
Jin'er?

86
00:07:30,690 --> 00:07:32,240
<i>Two!</i>

87
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,290
<i>Three!</i>

88
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,390
<i>Four!</i>

89
00:07:39,570 --> 00:07:41,560
<i>General!</i>

90
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:45,160
General, are you the only one who returned?

91
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:47,730
What's the matter?

92
00:07:47,730 --> 00:07:51,830
Did you expect that I would bring soldiers with me from the capital to suppress the Falcon Tribe?

93
00:07:51,830 --> 00:07:57,420
Or are you trying to say that the Chu Army is not as good as it was before my absence?

94
00:07:57,420 --> 00:07:59,160
Of course, that is not the case.

95
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:02,830
Then quickly update me on the military matters so I can formulate a strategy for the battle.

96
00:08:02,830 --> 00:08:04,380
Yes.

97
00:08:04,380 --> 00:08:08,030
In the beginning, there was only a small rebel army emerging from the Falcon Tribe.

98
00:08:08,030 --> 00:08:11,830
They used to be small in strength, but recently, a few factions have banded together

99
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:14,700
and various stragglers have been joining that army in rapid succession.

100
00:08:14,700 --> 00:08:16,950
Their military power has increased greatly.

101
00:08:18,210 --> 00:08:19,500
What about the chief of the Falcon Tribe?

102
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:22,690
Princess Ma Ya was the one who requested our aid this time.

103
00:08:22,690 --> 00:08:27,420
She says the goal of the rebel army is to wrest control of the political power within the Falcon Tribe.

104
00:08:27,420 --> 00:08:29,550
Oh, by the way!

105
00:08:29,550 --> 00:08:34,160
Princess Ma Ya has sent someone to inquire if Her Ladyship has returned?

106
00:08:35,670 --> 00:08:39,470
Is it you or the princess who wishes to know?

107
00:08:39,470 --> 00:08:41,960
Of course, it's the princess who wishes to know.

108
00:08:44,060 --> 00:08:47,760
Actually, we really miss Her Ladyship as well.

109
00:08:49,010 --> 00:08:51,290
Her Ladyship is with child, so it's inconvenient for her to travel far.

110
00:08:51,290 --> 00:08:53,950
She will return once she has given birth.

111
00:08:53,950 --> 00:08:55,470
Is that true?

112
00:08:55,470 --> 00:08:57,780
Congratulations, General!

113
00:09:00,090 --> 00:09:03,130
I can finally give Xiao Cong an explanation now.

114
00:09:03,130 --> 00:09:05,060
Xiao Cong?

115
00:09:08,130 --> 00:09:10,970
I will tell everyone the good news regarding Her Ladyship's pregnancy first,

116
00:09:10,970 --> 00:09:14,680
so that they all can be in a cheerful mood. So they can all be in a cheerful mood...

117
00:09:23,490 --> 00:09:27,030
Ever since the news of your pregnancy has been announced, everyone in the Rui Royal Manor,

118
00:09:27,030 --> 00:09:29,170
the high-ranking officials, and members of the aristocracy,

119
00:09:29,170 --> 00:09:34,070
and the very distant relatives have almost broken down the doors trying to congratulate you.

120
00:09:34,070 --> 00:09:37,270
Our general really does have a good amount of prestige.

121
00:09:37,270 --> 00:09:39,070
Look at all these snobs.

122
00:09:39,070 --> 00:09:42,790
They're only behaving in this manner because I'm the Great General Lord Yongning's Lady Wife.

123
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:45,290
They're all trying to seek profit by family ties and benefit at the expense of others.

124
00:09:45,290 --> 00:09:47,400
We didn't even receive a single needle from them

125
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:50,130
back when my mother and I were in dire straits.

126
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:53,150
That's true.

127
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:58,820
How's business at the fabric store these days?

128
00:09:58,820 --> 00:10:02,710
I've sent someone to keep an eye on it. If you're still uneasy about it, then I'll go there myself.

129
00:10:02,710 --> 00:10:04,800
Let's both go and take a look.

130
00:10:05,420 --> 00:10:07,050
You're thinking too much.

131
00:10:07,050 --> 00:10:11,090
The general has already said His Lady has to be well taken care of inside the manor.

132
00:10:11,090 --> 00:10:14,860
Nothing will happen to you if you secretly escape, but I will be the one who will suffer a calamity.

133
00:10:15,650 --> 00:10:18,620
The general is not even here. You should be listening to me instead.

134
00:10:18,620 --> 00:10:20,490
Whose servant girl are you, anyway?

135
00:10:20,490 --> 00:10:22,650
Why are you starting to sound more and more like the Great Demon King?

136
00:10:22,650 --> 00:10:25,550
Whoever spares my life will be my master.

137
00:10:26,860 --> 00:10:28,260
<i>Jin'er!</i>

138
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:30,360
Elder Sister Ruonan!

139
00:10:31,390 --> 00:10:33,160
Slowly.

140
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:35,480
- How have you been lately? <br> - Ruonan!

141
00:10:36,660 --> 00:10:38,650
I've been bored out of my mind for the past two weeks!

142
00:10:38,650 --> 00:10:41,670
I have nothing to do all day! All I've been doing is eating, eating, and more eating.

143
00:10:41,670 --> 00:10:43,280
Look! Haven't I gained weight?

144
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:45,170
You're pregnant. It's only natural for you to gain a little weight.

145
00:10:45,170 --> 00:10:47,250
- Is that so? <br> - Of course.

146
00:10:48,350 --> 00:10:50,350
Rou Rou, why are you just standing there?

147
00:10:50,350 --> 00:10:52,580
Quickly go and brew a good pot of tea for Elder Sister Ruonan to drink.

148
00:10:52,580 --> 00:10:55,190
You really have no tact at all.

149
00:10:57,270 --> 00:10:58,870
Did you have some free time today to visit me?

150
00:10:58,870 --> 00:11:01,770
I'd just received the armed escort and tidied all the new fabrics away

151
00:11:01,770 --> 00:11:03,290
when I thought of you and decided to come and visit you.

152
00:11:03,290 --> 00:11:06,750
I knew you must be bored, so I brought this girl with me to dispel your boredom.

153
00:11:06,750 --> 00:11:10,970
Lady Wife of the General, I wish you propitious good health.

154
00:11:10,970 --> 00:11:13,500
Little girl, you're so well-behaved.

155
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:17,110
This thing is adorable.

156
00:11:17,110 --> 00:11:18,440
What is it called?

157
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:20,430
I should plant some in my garden soon.

158
00:11:20,430 --> 00:11:22,510
I'm not very familiar with things related to flora.

159
00:11:22,510 --> 00:11:24,620
The child probably picked them at random along the mountain path.

160
00:11:24,620 --> 00:11:28,070
We have lots of these plants in my village.

161
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:33,060
Is that so? Then I'll have to go there and take a look.

162
00:11:33,060 --> 00:11:35,490
Ruonan, take me there.

163
00:11:35,490 --> 00:11:37,950
How am I going to explain myself to the general if I take you out of the manor?

164
00:11:37,950 --> 00:11:41,580
The general isn't here! No one's here except for me.

165
00:11:42,250 --> 00:11:44,090
All right. Let's go, then.

166
00:11:44,090 --> 00:11:47,340
- This is great! Quickly, let's go, let's go, let's go. <br> - Not so fast.

167
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:49,410
- Hurry up! <br> - Let's go.

168
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:01,530
Miss!

169
00:12:04,460 --> 00:12:06,290
Be careful.

170
00:12:06,290 --> 00:12:09,850
It's here. There are flowers here.

171
00:12:10,460 --> 00:12:13,590
It looks like the flower season is over. I came too late.

172
00:12:13,590 --> 00:12:17,600
Then next time, I'll tell you earlier so you can come and see them.

173
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:22,570
That is...

174
00:12:22,570 --> 00:12:26,790
He is Uncle Hua. He planted all of these flowers.

175
00:12:29,950 --> 00:12:33,640
Sister Ruonan, why don't you take me to the textile store?

176
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:37,780
I haven't gone there for a while. I keep thinking about it!

177
00:12:37,780 --> 00:12:40,630
Let's go.

178
00:12:46,370 --> 00:12:48,840
<i>[Jin'er Textile Shop]</i>

179
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:53,560
Let me tell you! To every lady who came to visit the child in my belly,

180
00:12:53,560 --> 00:12:55,120
I mentioned my shop!

181
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:57,520
I never imagined they'd all come to buy fabric!

182
00:12:57,520 --> 00:13:02,470
I was wondering why you had so many customers! So that's what you did!

183
00:13:02,470 --> 00:13:08,240
Your business in the capital is lively and flourishing.

184
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:11,270
My business is doing well, but I'm always at home.

185
00:13:11,270 --> 00:13:13,790
How would I have time to manage it?

186
00:13:15,930 --> 00:13:20,480
Ruonan, why don't you watch it for me? I'll share the profits with you!

187
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:24,240
What are you saying? It's your money. I can't take it.

188
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:27,750
What are you saying? We're going to be one family soon!

189
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:32,550
You and Xiuyuan can become one, so our shops can also do the same!

190
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:34,990
Let us obtain the palace's order together!

191
00:13:34,990 --> 00:13:37,630
We'll have lots of businesses in the future!

192
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:40,850
Besides, aren't you preparing to open a second shop?

193
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:45,320
Your explanation does make some sense.

194
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:47,660
Sister-in-Law. Miss Ruonan.

195
00:13:47,660 --> 00:13:49,300
Xiuyuan?

196
00:13:49,300 --> 00:13:51,440
You don't focus on your own work.

197
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:53,100
Instead, you came over to the textile shop.

198
00:13:53,100 --> 00:13:55,940
Be careful, I might report you to the general when he gets back.

199
00:13:55,940 --> 00:13:59,510
Sister-in-Law, spare me! I'll leave after I have a cup of tea.

200
00:14:05,800 --> 00:14:09,360
Didn't Brother forbid you from going outside? What are you doing here?

201
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:12,650
Hey! I have official matters!

202
00:14:12,650 --> 00:14:15,450
General told me to be good and stay at home.

203
00:14:15,450 --> 00:14:18,080
There's no one to care for the shop's business!

204
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:20,660
So, I decided

205
00:14:20,660 --> 00:14:24,100
that Jin'er Textile Shop and Ruonan Textile shop will merge into one.

206
00:14:24,100 --> 00:14:26,840
This way, it can solve my worries about the shop.

207
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:30,170
And my shop can also be expanded under Ruonan's watch!

208
00:14:30,170 --> 00:14:33,110
Sister-in-Law, you mean you want to merge the shops?

209
00:14:33,110 --> 00:14:35,780
- Ruonan will look after both? <br> - Right.

210
00:14:36,640 --> 00:14:38,800
Sister-in-Law, you worked so hard for the textile shop.

211
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:41,530
Is it really okay to hand it over to another person?

212
00:14:41,530 --> 00:14:43,310
How can Ruonan count as "another"?

213
00:14:43,310 --> 00:14:46,040
She's your future wife!

214
00:14:46,870 --> 00:14:50,970
Then, won't that make Ruonan even busier?

215
00:14:51,830 --> 00:14:54,460
No one is asking for your opinion!

216
00:14:54,460 --> 00:14:56,730
Ruonan, what do you think?

217
00:14:56,730 --> 00:14:59,640
How could I refuse Little Sister Jin'er's request?

218
00:14:59,640 --> 00:15:02,580
Then once things are settled, I'll come let you know!

219
00:15:02,580 --> 00:15:04,740
This is great!

220
00:15:10,020 --> 00:15:11,930
You only stopped by for some tea, right?

221
00:15:11,930 --> 00:15:14,250
You're done drinking, you can go now.

222
00:15:14,250 --> 00:15:16,150
Sister-in-Law, I'm not done yet.

223
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:18,960
I'll stay with Miss Ruonan for a little while longer.

224
00:15:19,630 --> 00:15:21,570
Miss Ruonan.

225
00:15:29,100 --> 00:15:33,470
Mother! Don't! Don't! Mother, I was wrong!

226
00:15:33,470 --> 00:15:36,410
I won't do it again, I'll be good from now on!

227
00:15:36,410 --> 00:15:39,000
Enough, enough. I'll deal with you once I get back.

228
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:41,000
Come with me to Rui Royal Manor.

229
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:43,690
- Is it that serious? <br> - Come on.

230
00:15:44,890 --> 00:15:47,730
A girl came here with this letter in hand. <br> <i>[To my wife, Jin'er...]</i>

231
00:15:47,730 --> 00:15:50,090
She said it was arranged by a court official.

232
00:15:50,090 --> 00:15:52,480
She also said Lord Yongning has already taken her in. <br> <i>(T/N: Meaning he's slept with her and has taken her as a concubine.)</i>

233
00:15:52,480 --> 00:15:56,590
And he told her Lady Yongning will take care of her if she came with his letter.

234
00:15:56,590 --> 00:16:01,770
This girl says she is pregnant with Lord Yongning's child.

235
00:16:04,340 --> 00:16:06,360
Where is that girl?

236
00:16:07,170 --> 00:16:09,550
Bring her in!

237
00:16:09,550 --> 00:16:10,970
Jin'er.

238
00:16:10,970 --> 00:16:13,110
It's all right, Mother.

239
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:18,490
If my daughter is not happy about this, we can find a place for her in the village.

240
00:16:18,490 --> 00:16:23,570
I believe Son-in-Law will not argue with you over this girl.

241
00:16:23,570 --> 00:16:25,520
Don't worry, Royal Father.

242
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:40,100
You're pregnant, too?

243
00:16:42,060 --> 00:16:45,400
Greetings, Lady Yongning.

244
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:48,570
Since you are pregnant, don't kneel.

245
00:16:48,570 --> 00:16:50,680
Thank you, My Lady.

246
00:16:50,680 --> 00:16:53,130
I'll ask you a few questions.

247
00:16:53,130 --> 00:16:57,860
If you dare lie, I'll have someone flog you!

248
00:16:57,860 --> 00:17:00,700
My Royal Father and Consort Mother are both here.

249
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:02,690
My husband is not here,

250
00:17:02,690 --> 00:17:05,090
but I have plenty of backing.

251
00:17:05,770 --> 00:17:11,220
Jin'er, don't worry. I will definitely get justice for you.

252
00:17:11,220 --> 00:17:14,650
I do not dare to keep any secrets.

253
00:17:17,420 --> 00:17:19,860
You're really pregnant?

254
00:17:19,860 --> 00:17:24,130
If you do not believe me, you can summon a physician.

255
00:17:24,130 --> 00:17:27,980
Then it looks like it's true. Then you cannot be flogged.

256
00:17:27,980 --> 00:17:30,870
So what if she's pregnant?

257
00:17:30,870 --> 00:17:34,890
Royal Father, the child is innocent.

258
00:17:36,550 --> 00:17:39,040
My Jin'er's heart is too kind.

259
00:17:39,040 --> 00:17:42,830
That's why these nobodies all dare to come here.

260
00:17:42,830 --> 00:17:45,060
Look at her.

261
00:17:45,060 --> 00:17:48,460
She's clearly not a proper girl.

262
00:17:51,790 --> 00:17:54,310
If I had a choice,

263
00:17:54,310 --> 00:17:57,310
no one would be willing to be like this!

264
00:17:58,710 --> 00:18:02,520
Originally, I was from a good family, too!

265
00:18:02,520 --> 00:18:05,020
My father was a scholar, too!

266
00:18:05,030 --> 00:18:09,660
But who would have imagined, with one natural disaster...!

267
00:18:10,770 --> 00:18:14,350
Do you want to drink some water before you continue?

268
00:18:14,350 --> 00:18:17,070
There's no need, My Lady.

269
00:18:17,070 --> 00:18:21,090
I was too emotional. Please be understanding.

270
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:25,310
The letter told you to find Lady Yongning.

271
00:18:25,310 --> 00:18:27,520
- Right? <br> - Yes.

272
00:18:30,840 --> 00:18:34,180
Then you are from the capital?

273
00:18:34,180 --> 00:18:39,890
I am not from the capital. This is my first time here.

274
00:18:39,890 --> 00:18:42,660
Then, to find Lady Yongning...

275
00:18:42,660 --> 00:18:45,740
why did you come to Rui Royal Manor?

276
00:18:47,070 --> 00:18:51,020
Why didn't you go to Lord Yongning's manor?

277
00:18:53,990 --> 00:18:58,860
I heard Lady Yongning was at Rui Royal Manor,

278
00:18:58,860 --> 00:19:01,670
- so that's why I came here. <br> - Oh?

279
00:19:01,670 --> 00:19:05,630
I don't understand what you were thinking.

280
00:19:06,540 --> 00:19:11,980
But because you knew I was at my maternal home

281
00:19:11,980 --> 00:19:14,680
that's why you came to Rui Royal Manor, right?

282
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:16,550
Yes.

283
00:19:18,990 --> 00:19:20,310
My Lady,

284
00:19:20,310 --> 00:19:23,530
- then you sure are stupid! <br> - Why is Jin'er saying that?

285
00:19:23,530 --> 00:19:26,020
If you really are carrying my husband's child,

286
00:19:26,020 --> 00:19:30,580
did you come here hoping my parents would get justice for you?

287
00:19:31,600 --> 00:19:35,090
Since my husband slept with you,

288
00:19:35,090 --> 00:19:37,910
then do you remember

289
00:19:37,910 --> 00:19:42,430
that there's a birthmark on my husband's left hip?

290
00:19:43,930 --> 00:19:48,130
The light was off then, I couldn't see clearly.

291
00:19:48,130 --> 00:19:51,150
I could only see part of him.

292
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:57,610
Who told you to come here? Tell me.

293
00:19:58,480 --> 00:20:00,700
I don't know what you're talking about.

294
00:20:00,700 --> 00:20:05,070
My husband doesn't have a birthmark, I was lying to you!

295
00:20:05,070 --> 00:20:09,890
How dare you! Do you think my Rui Royal Manor is nothing?

296
00:20:09,890 --> 00:20:13,840
Royal Father, please be calm. Let her explain.

297
00:20:15,100 --> 00:20:18,700
Miss, if you tell me,

298
00:20:18,700 --> 00:20:23,830
I will capture the person who ordered you and send that person to be flogged at the magistrate's office.

299
00:20:23,830 --> 00:20:27,530
If you don't tell me, I won't flog you.

300
00:20:27,530 --> 00:20:32,270
I'll send you to the magistrate and tell him you stole things in the Royal Manor!

301
00:20:33,230 --> 00:20:36,980
I really don't know who it is!

302
00:20:37,760 --> 00:20:41,420
Looks like she won't tell us who is behind this.

303
00:20:41,420 --> 00:20:44,130
Why don't we send her straight to the magistrate?

304
00:20:44,130 --> 00:20:47,360
Perhaps the people there will have a way to make her speak the truth?

305
00:20:47,360 --> 00:20:49,470
I really don't know!

306
00:20:49,470 --> 00:20:54,160
I originally became pregnant with a customer's child and was about to abort it!

307
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:56,730
But someone bought me from the brothel at the last minute!

308
00:20:56,730 --> 00:21:01,280
That person had the deed to my body, I had to listen to him!

309
00:21:01,280 --> 00:21:03,270
My Lady!

310
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:06,600
How cruel!

311
00:21:06,600 --> 00:21:08,860
Thankfully, our Jin has a good temper.

312
00:21:08,860 --> 00:21:12,880
She could've been emotionally distraught, and it would've affected her baby!

313
00:21:13,610 --> 00:21:16,570
Servants! Bring the painter here!

314
00:21:16,570 --> 00:21:20,300
Draw the person she is talking about!

315
00:21:21,220 --> 00:21:24,780
Hurry and leave. After all, you are still pregnant.

316
00:21:36,030 --> 00:21:38,480
Did His Lordship have any other things to say?

317
00:21:41,460 --> 00:21:45,480
It looks like it is time to make a move.

318
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:55,960
Who hates my Jin'er so much?

319
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:57,900
These are tough tactics,

320
00:21:57,900 --> 00:22:01,960
but to a person who just became pregnant and doesn't have a husband by her side,

321
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:05,150
it is very useful.

322
00:22:06,430 --> 00:22:09,820
Mother, don't worry. Didn't I tell you?

323
00:22:09,820 --> 00:22:12,570
My husband wouldn't fall for people like that.

324
00:22:12,570 --> 00:22:17,220
That's right! General wouldn't like those low-class girls.

325
00:22:18,250 --> 00:22:23,130
Seeing how good your relationship is, I'm at ease.

326
00:22:25,500 --> 00:22:27,590
That's right, Jin'er.

327
00:22:27,590 --> 00:22:31,850
Who do you think was behind today's incident?

328
00:22:44,230 --> 00:22:48,930
Jing'er, look. Do you know her?

329
00:22:53,810 --> 00:22:56,230
It's... not very clear.

330
00:22:56,230 --> 00:22:58,070
Tell the truth!

331
00:23:00,980 --> 00:23:05,460
It looks like... Auntie Liu from Sister Zi's room.

332
00:23:05,460 --> 00:23:08,150
I think it looks like Auntie Liu, too.

333
00:23:08,150 --> 00:23:10,700
Because Auntie Liu has a mole by her eyebrow.

334
00:23:10,700 --> 00:23:13,060
It's a bit lower, near her brow.

335
00:23:13,060 --> 00:23:14,380
How ridiculous!

336
00:23:14,380 --> 00:23:18,440
Such an embarrassing thing happened in Rui Royal Manor!

337
00:23:18,440 --> 00:23:20,560
If anything had really happened to Jin'er,

338
00:23:20,560 --> 00:23:23,950
would Chu Xiuming have spared us all?

339
00:23:24,930 --> 00:23:28,240
As the royal consort, this is your fault! <br> <i>(T/N: Consort is responsible for domestic matters.)</i>

340
00:23:45,450 --> 00:23:47,360
Jing'er!

341
00:23:47,360 --> 00:23:52,350
Is this just because of that one slap from Zi'er? Is it worth it?

342
00:23:52,350 --> 00:23:55,600
Besides, there's no scar on your face.

343
00:23:58,050 --> 00:24:01,970
If this incident really brings shame to the royal manor,

344
00:24:01,970 --> 00:24:04,560
do not blame me for being cruel.

345
00:24:06,980 --> 00:24:09,090
I know.

346
00:24:11,280 --> 00:24:13,080
You may leave.

347
00:24:23,040 --> 00:24:26,060
<i>Good!</i>

348
00:24:29,700 --> 00:24:31,880
<i>Good!</i>

349
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:40,600
<i>Great!</i>

350
00:24:54,280 --> 00:24:59,780
<i>Good!</i>

351
00:25:10,410 --> 00:25:13,330
<i>[Jǐnxiù Huázhāng Textile Shop]</i>

352
00:25:14,080 --> 00:25:20,440
<i>Good!</i>

353
00:25:23,480 --> 00:25:26,950
From today on, Jin'er Textile Shop and Ruonan Textile Shop

354
00:25:26,950 --> 00:25:29,720
will become Jǐnxiù Huázhāng Textile Shop.

355
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:33,360
There will be a ten percent discount on the new fabrics today.

356
00:25:33,360 --> 00:25:35,520
I hope everyone can come and support us!

357
00:25:35,520 --> 00:25:37,090
Please come and support us!

358
00:25:37,090 --> 00:25:42,340
<i>Good!</i>

359
00:25:47,940 --> 00:25:52,230
<i>[Jǐnxiù Huázhāng Textile Shop]</i>

360
00:25:53,940 --> 00:25:55,860
Sister Jin!

361
00:25:59,230 --> 00:26:00,870
Congratulations on your new shop!

362
00:26:00,870 --> 00:26:04,520
Royal Father told us to bring congratulatory gifts!

363
00:26:04,520 --> 00:26:06,100
If you two create more trouble today,

364
00:26:06,100 --> 00:26:10,430
when General comes back, you will both lose an arm!

365
00:26:10,430 --> 00:26:12,580
Little Sister Jin, I haven't said a single word.

366
00:26:12,580 --> 00:26:15,060
I didn't offend you.

367
00:26:15,060 --> 00:26:17,410
What counts as offending?

368
00:26:17,410 --> 00:26:19,490
I accept your goodwill.

369
00:26:19,490 --> 00:26:22,470
Forget about these gifts.

370
00:26:22,470 --> 00:26:24,940
If anything happens to the general's child in my belly,

371
00:26:24,940 --> 00:26:28,930
other people, not knowing better, might think there was a problem with the gifts!

372
00:26:30,330 --> 00:26:33,090
You Shen Jin! You don't have to accept them!

373
00:26:33,090 --> 00:26:36,190
I only came out of respect for Father!

374
00:26:36,190 --> 00:26:37,850
Let's go!

375
00:26:40,980 --> 00:26:44,020
That brat! She became more capable in a few days! <br> <i>[Yi Huan Bridge]</i>

376
00:26:44,020 --> 00:26:46,170
I haven't even gotten back at her for what happened last time!

377
00:26:46,170 --> 00:26:49,960
I came here to make peace with her and she even dares to mock me.

378
00:26:49,960 --> 00:26:52,050
Sister Zi!

379
00:26:52,050 --> 00:26:55,990
I never imagined Shen Jin would really become a phoenix. <br><i> (T/N: become someone of great importance)</i>

380
00:26:55,990 --> 00:26:59,530
Every official in the capital thinks highly of her now.

381
00:26:59,530 --> 00:27:05,460
All of the noble first ladies are rushing to invite her to their homes for a visit! <i> (T/N: "official first wives" with authority)</i>

382
00:27:05,460 --> 00:27:09,250
Say, Chu Xiuming really is capable.

383
00:27:09,250 --> 00:27:11,960
He not only has earned great merit in war, but in a short period of time,

384
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:14,290
he has obtained all the scholarly officials' approval, too!

385
00:27:14,290 --> 00:27:17,960
He really has become the most famous person in the capital!

386
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:20,190
What's so great about that?

387
00:27:20,190 --> 00:27:22,260
Let's see how long he can be arrogant for!

388
00:27:22,260 --> 00:27:27,550
Older Sister, I heard that Shen Jin's store is making a fortune, too.

389
00:27:27,550 --> 00:27:30,960
Last time, her fabrics sold out by noon.

390
00:27:30,960 --> 00:27:34,630
There's also a continuous flow of people from outside the city who want to buy them.

391
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:38,560
Even though we are all from the Rui Royal Manor,

392
00:27:38,560 --> 00:27:42,470
she married into the general's manor and earns money on her own.

393
00:27:42,470 --> 00:27:45,950
I really do envy her a little.

394
00:27:45,950 --> 00:27:48,450
What's there to envy?

395
00:27:49,310 --> 00:27:52,340
Sister, we are still unmarried.

396
00:27:52,340 --> 00:27:53,820
But who knows?

397
00:27:53,820 --> 00:27:57,540
If we get married and merely sit at home, eating away at our resources,

398
00:27:57,540 --> 00:27:59,690
only living off of our dowries,

399
00:27:59,690 --> 00:28:02,490
and needing our husband's permission for everything...

400
00:28:02,490 --> 00:28:04,850
That must feel awful.

401
00:28:04,850 --> 00:28:08,090
What? Even you are laughing at me that I can't get married?

402
00:28:08,090 --> 00:28:10,060
Sister, what are you saying?

403
00:28:10,060 --> 00:28:14,680
I think this is unfair to you!

404
00:28:14,680 --> 00:28:20,890
This marriage was originally yours, right?

405
00:28:20,890 --> 00:28:24,700
Due to a freak accident, Shen Jin took your place instead.

406
00:28:24,700 --> 00:28:27,050
She got the greatest advantage!

407
00:28:27,050 --> 00:28:30,560
Chu Xiuming should be your husband.

408
00:28:30,560 --> 00:28:35,350
The lady of the general's manor should be you.

409
00:28:35,350 --> 00:28:39,530
If you were the lady of the general's manor today,

410
00:28:39,530 --> 00:28:41,730
where would Shen Jin even be?

411
00:28:41,730 --> 00:28:45,640
I think even General would have to show you some respect.

412
00:28:46,990 --> 00:28:52,720
That's right. I should have been the general's lady!

413
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:58,030
<i>[Yi Huan Bridge]</i>

414
00:28:58,710 --> 00:29:02,850
Even the wife this Great General married is quite shrewd.

415
00:29:02,850 --> 00:29:04,060
These two lovers.

416
00:29:04,060 --> 00:29:08,670
One holds military power and one holds monetary power.

417
00:29:08,670 --> 00:29:11,670
Could they be

418
00:29:11,670 --> 00:29:15,550
preparing to take the empire from Your Majesty?

419
00:29:15,550 --> 00:29:17,490
You are worrying too much.

420
00:29:17,490 --> 00:29:19,920
How much money can a textile shop earn?

421
00:29:19,920 --> 00:29:25,400
Your Majesty, a textile shop is not a small business.

422
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:29,720
All of the royal palace's textiles are from this shop.

423
00:29:29,720 --> 00:29:33,920
All the fabric comes from the general's lady.

424
00:29:35,750 --> 00:29:39,040
Oh? Is that so?

425
00:29:39,770 --> 00:29:45,410
Lord Yongning's little wife has done a great job with her business.

426
00:29:45,410 --> 00:29:48,690
All the money has entered the general's manor.

427
00:29:50,110 --> 00:29:56,300
One day, won't it become easier to buy horses and soldiers?

428
00:29:57,440 --> 00:29:59,120
Your Majesty,

429
00:29:59,120 --> 00:30:04,570
I believe this woman is also problematic.

430
00:30:04,570 --> 00:30:07,480
Shen Jin is the second daughter of Rui Royal Manor.

431
00:30:07,480 --> 00:30:10,470
I was the one who arranged this marriage.

432
00:30:10,470 --> 00:30:13,860
I have not seen Prince Rui for a while.

433
00:30:13,860 --> 00:30:16,330
- Eunuch Li. <br> - Here.

434
00:30:16,330 --> 00:30:19,440
I will invite Prince Rui and his family for a feast tomorrow

435
00:30:19,440 --> 00:30:21,920
to congratulate the general's lady on her pregnancy.

436
00:30:21,920 --> 00:30:23,420
Yes.

437
00:30:33,130 --> 00:30:35,860
<i>Fight! Fight!</i>

438
00:30:35,860 --> 00:30:38,760
Even His Majesty is going to celebrate Shen Jin, too.

439
00:30:38,760 --> 00:30:41,840
He told our family to attend the banquet, too.

440
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:44,020
How amazing.

441
00:30:44,020 --> 00:30:46,080
It's because she's the general's lady.

442
00:30:46,080 --> 00:30:49,870
If she was just a little daughter from the family, who would care?

443
00:30:49,870 --> 00:30:51,040
That's true.

444
00:30:51,040 --> 00:30:55,110
But if the emperor threw a feast just for you today,

445
00:30:55,110 --> 00:30:58,510
who in court wouldn't come to make connections with you?

446
00:30:59,700 --> 00:31:04,460
The thing that went wrong was Shen Jin entering the marriage palanquin instead.

447
00:31:04,460 --> 00:31:06,630
I should have been the general's lady.

448
00:31:06,630 --> 00:31:09,390
If everyone didn't call him "Devil General, Devil General,"

449
00:31:09,390 --> 00:31:11,850
would she have had a chance?

450
00:31:14,200 --> 00:31:17,150
Sister, it's not too late now.

451
00:31:17,150 --> 00:31:22,020
If His Majesty knows Shen Jin took your place on purpose,

452
00:31:22,020 --> 00:31:23,740
that would be the crime of lying to the emperor!

453
00:31:23,740 --> 00:31:26,640
He would strip her skin off!

454
00:31:27,910 --> 00:31:30,810
Shen Jin took my place on purpose?

455
00:31:31,760 --> 00:31:34,080
Think about it. Besides the entire Rui Royal Manor,

456
00:31:34,080 --> 00:31:36,880
who knows how Shen Jin ended up in the marriage palanquin?

457
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:40,390
Also, Royal Father favors you. Of course, he'd protect you.

458
00:31:40,390 --> 00:31:44,040
When that happens, you'll become the general's lady.

459
00:31:47,850 --> 00:31:49,640
That's right!

460
00:31:53,100 --> 00:31:55,900
Yesterday, I heard Mother talking about Danqiao.

461
00:31:55,900 --> 00:31:59,900
I really didn't expect Shen Zi to do something so dirty.

462
00:31:59,900 --> 00:32:01,910
I'm furious, too.

463
00:32:01,910 --> 00:32:03,800
We are sisters,

464
00:32:03,800 --> 00:32:06,500
but we keep fighting.

465
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:08,700
It's really such an embarrassment to the Rui Royal Manor.

466
00:32:09,600 --> 00:32:11,000
Talking about embarrassment,

467
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:14,800
naturally, it's the daughter of a woman who washes feet who is the most shameless.

468
00:32:14,800 --> 00:32:16,700
You are going overboard.

469
00:32:16,700 --> 00:32:19,200
I went overboard?

470
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:22,400
Because of you, I was scolded by Royal Father for no good reason!

471
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:24,500
I took the initiative to make peace with you and you even insulted me.

472
00:32:24,500 --> 00:32:27,000
You are such a calculating woman.

473
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:30,400
Younger Sister, can we not embarrass the family in public?

474
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:34,600
You can say whatever you want but don't involve my mother.

475
00:32:34,600 --> 00:32:37,400
Before you got married, you were just a pug by my side.

476
00:32:37,400 --> 00:32:40,100
Now that you are the general's wife, you are even wagging your tail. <i>(T/N: hinting that she's proud)</i>

477
00:32:40,100 --> 00:32:42,600
You are the same level as that foot wash--

478
00:32:44,700 --> 00:32:45,800
You slapped me?

479
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:49,500
Stop messing around, all right? Can't you see where we are now?

480
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:55,400
You...

481
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:07,200
Younger Sister, don't be angry.

482
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:09,800
You are now a pregnant woman.

483
00:33:09,800 --> 00:33:12,900
Older Sister, don't worry. I know.

484
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:20,000
For our future children, if they're a boy and a girl,

485
