should we arrange for them to get married?

486
00:33:21,800 --> 00:33:25,800
This way, we will be even closer.

487
00:33:26,700 --> 00:33:29,100
Older Sister, I think that

488
00:33:29,100 --> 00:33:31,800
when a person is most powerless,

489
00:33:31,800 --> 00:33:34,100
is when they don't have a choice.

490
00:33:34,800 --> 00:33:39,600
Although my child is unable to choose whether to be born or not,

491
00:33:39,600 --> 00:33:43,100
but as a mother, the only thing I can do,

492
00:33:43,100 --> 00:33:45,500
except for protecting him,

493
00:33:45,500 --> 00:33:49,600
is that I want to let my child make his own choices in life.

494
00:33:49,600 --> 00:33:52,270
After all, not everyone can be like us

495
00:33:52,270 --> 00:33:55,400
who are so blessed in marriage.

496
00:33:56,300 --> 00:33:58,400
You are right.

497
00:33:58,400 --> 00:33:59,670
Let's do this.

498
00:33:59,670 --> 00:34:02,600
If there's mutual consent between them, we will let them be together.

499
00:34:02,600 --> 00:34:06,300
If they don't, we won't force them.

500
00:34:06,300 --> 00:34:10,300
I think it's like how among so many sisters, you dote on me the most.

501
00:34:10,300 --> 00:34:12,500
This is fate.

502
00:34:12,500 --> 00:34:16,400
The children have their own fates, too.

503
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:19,100
You're just a sweet talker.

504
00:34:22,200 --> 00:34:24,800
Greetings, Your Majesty.

505
00:34:26,600 --> 00:34:28,000
You may rise.

506
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:30,200
Thank you, Your Majesty.

507
00:34:30,200 --> 00:34:33,100
There's good news from the border today.

508
00:34:33,100 --> 00:34:36,400
Lord Yongning wiped out the rebels from the Hawk Clan.

509
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:41,000
There's an old saying that if the family lives in harmony, all affairs will prosper. Only when the family is in harmony,

510
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:43,800
when the soldiers fight to serve the Imperial Court,

511
00:34:43,800 --> 00:34:46,300
they will do it with all of their might.

512
00:34:46,300 --> 00:34:49,000
To show the Imperial Court's kindness and favor,

513
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:51,500
I confer the second daughter of Prince of Rui,

514
00:34:51,500 --> 00:34:55,600
the wife of Chu Xiuming, Lord Yongning as a court lady.

515
00:34:58,300 --> 00:35:01,600
Looks like my family has another court lady.

516
00:35:01,600 --> 00:35:03,100
I thank you, Your Majesty.

517
00:35:03,100 --> 00:35:05,100
I thank you, Your Majesty.

518
00:35:05,780 --> 00:35:08,470
Your Majesty, you can't do this!

